window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Seizure</i> is the ongoing story of Chris, experienced academic and up-and-coming freelance graphic designer with epilepsy seeking new design projects daily and ultimately his own lifestyle in York, Pennsylvania.</p> <p>It is the story of Michael, his former best friend, and of how both men will decide how involved each will be in their separate lives.</p> <p>It is the ongoing story of Mary Grace, how she will grow increasingly involved in Chris's medical affairs, and of whether or not it will be a good thing.</p> <p>It is the story of Burke and Bender, two bowling league teammates who offer support and a different perspective to Chris.</p> <p>It is a reminder of facing challenges, growth and adaptation, and the importance of constantly moving forward in life.</p>"; 
